  "factionId": "SM",
  "sourceId": "000000021",
  "legend": "Every Blood Angel felt their hopes dashed when the first of the Primaris Space Marines brought to the Chapter by Roboute Guilliman fell to the Black Rage. With great solemnity were these brothers inducted into the Death Company. Their strength, combined with the fury of the Black Rage, is a terrifying sight to behold.",
